<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>日常 on 元视角</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8/</link><description>Recent content in 日常 on 元视角</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 14:44:01 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>似花还似非花</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/like-flowers-not-flowers/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Nov 2022 12:30:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/like-flowers-not-flowers/</guid><description>周末独自前往大唐芙蓉园，心中盘桓已久的想法，于此时此地显得不合时宜，因为无论是指渐渐转凉的天气，还是指此消彼长的疫情，都俨然有一点沉默和突兀。更不必说，冬天的雾霾会让整个城市呼吸困难，蓝色的口罩像一张巨网，将相关或者不相关的人们笼络于其中。</description></item></channel></rss>